---
import { Button } from "@openmarch/ui";
import { ArrowRightIcon } from "@phosphor-icons/react";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import carolineHs from "@/assets/testimonials/caroline.jpg";
---

<section id="testimonials" class="flex flex-col gap-8 items-center">
    <h1 class="text-h3">Changing how ensembles design and perform</h1>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 max-[920px]:grid-cols-1 gap-8">
        <div
            class="bg-fg-1 border border-stroke justify-center row-span-2 rounded-6 p-12 flex flex-col gap-6"
        >
            <h2 class="text-h4">Sunbright HS</h2>
            <p class="text-body font-medium">Brandon Wright, Marching Band</p>
            <p class="text-body leading-[165%] text-text-subtitle">
                We’re a small K-12 school of about 470 students, with 25 in the
                high school band. I’ve tried every program we could afford, and
                OpenMarch has been the most accessible and easy to use. It’s
                been a lifesaver.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div
            class="bg-fg-1 border border-stroke justify-center rounded-6 p-12 flex flex-col gap-6"
        >
            <h2 class="text-h4">Cinnaminson HS</h2>
            <p class="text-body font-medium">Douglas Ferraro, Indoor</p>
            <p class="text-body leading-[165%] text-text-subtitle">
                I only write drill during indoor season and couldn’t justify the
                cost of other software. I saw a post about OpenMarch and gave it
                a shot! We finished writing & teaching the show earlier than
                ever before, and the students were loving the dot sheets and
                watching the drill on the big screen! I would absolutely
                recommend it, especially for smaller ensembles and new drill
                writers.
            </p>
        </div>

        <a
            href="/blog/2025-11-10-caroline-hss-visit"
            class="bg-fg-1 border border-accent justify-center items-center rounded-6 p-12 flex flex-col max-[510px]items-start hover:brightness-110 duration-150 active:scale-95 ease-out"
        >
            <Image
                src={carolineHs}
                alt="Caroline HS"
                class="object-cover rounded-8"
                width={256}
                height={128}
            />
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                <h2 class="text-h4">Caroline HS</h2>
                <p class="text-body font-medium">Carter King, Outdoor</p>
                <p class="text-body leading-[165%] text-text-subtitle">
                    Read this article on how OpenMarch helped the Caroline High
                    School marching band in the 2025 season.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                    Read more <ArrowRightIcon size={24} />
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
